trans-unit.source: Examination administration for martial arts clubs

Welcome to our exam admin! What is this all about? This is a progressive web app for administrating martial arts exams. You can: Create martial arts Create exams Create user accounts Users can register themselfs as participants for an existing exam Examiners can upload exam results and upload a protocol for each user
Please type in a correct email!
You need to type in your password...
Sorry, but you don't have any exam results yet!
Hello, ! Here you can add a new club to your profile, if you want!
Hello, ! Here you can add a new martial art to your profile, if you want!
Has the user passed this exam?
Please choose the new rank of the user!
Protocol upload - Please choose a file.
This means that either you have not yet created an exam, or each participant already has their exam result.
Hello, examiner! You can see your participants listed below.
I'm sorry, but you do not have the required minimum rank.
Do you really want to delete this exam?

With the form below you can create a new exam!
Please choose a martial art for this exam!
Tell us, in a few words, what this exam is all about
Please enter a title with at least 10 characters!
Put every important detail into here
Please enter a description with at least 15 characters!
Please set a min rank! You can set it to "none", if there is no min rank.
Please set time and date when the exam should start!
Please set time and date when registration should close!
Please enter a price! 0,00€ or 0.00€ would be ok.
Please choose a name for this martial art!
Please choose a style name for this martial art!

How many ranks do you want to add?
You can add as many ranks as you need.
Hints: Ranks are sortet from lowest to highest. You should stick to this order to avoid errors. You can rearrange items with drag and drop!
